chuette</span>&nbsp;<span class=\"hcdict\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">divided</span>&nbsp;<span class=\"hcdict\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Republicans</span>&nbsp;<span class=\"hcdict\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">and</span><span class=\"hcdict\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">undermined</span>&nbsp;<span class=\"hcdict highlight\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(2, 67, 130); font-weight: bold;\">enthusiasm</span>&nbsp;<span class=\"hcdict\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">in</span>&nbsp;<span class=\"hcdict\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">the</span>&nbsp;<span class=\"hcdict\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">November</span>&nbsp;<span class=\"hcdict\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">elections</span>.</p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(40, 40, 40); font-family: verdana, &quot;ms song&quot;; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span class=\"hcdict\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Is</span>&nbsp;<span class=\"hcdict\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">he</span>&nbsp;<span class=\"hcdict\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">leaving</span>&nbsp;<span class=\"hcdict\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">office</span>&nbsp;<span class=\"hcdict\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">with</span>&nbsp;<span class=\"hcdict\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">Michigan</span>&nbsp;<span class=\"hcdict\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">in</span>&nbsp;<span class=\"hcdict\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">better</span>&nbsp;<span class=\"hcdict\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">shape</span>&nbsp;<span class=\"hcdict\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">than</span>&nbsp;<span class=\"hcdict\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">he</span>&nbsp;<span class=\"hcdict\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">found</span>&nbsp;<span class=\"hcdict\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\">it</span>?&nbsp;<